{"tid":2004553,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"689因肥佬黎出櫃 - 陳也","createTime":"2020-05-06T13:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T13:43:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1c113af6fbe07cf6d14b84fbf8e8ccc2b0485f6f","tid":2004553,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T13:42:24.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200506/20912680/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200506%2F20912680%2F&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=52848ed6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200506%2F20912680%2F&h=4e716f47\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200506/20912680/</a><br />\n<br />\n689因肥佬黎出櫃 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200506/large/1588663701_bd9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200506%2Flarge%2F1588663701_bd9c.jpg&h=2567f97f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請邁克專業評審，689係咪同志現形，戀上了肥佬黎？冇七成，都有五成吧。否則冇理由下下啄住肥佬黎背後，chur到盡，每日。。。。。。。。。。。再出發嗎？689未出發，先出櫃，背棄了龍蝦，換了重口味的肥佬，狼，肉食性嘛。<br />\n<br />\n見五一黃店周好景，689煽惑散仔「裝修黃店」，實名舉報僭建排。。。。。。。。。。。差佬貪方便偷走雪糕筒自用的「罪行」被斷正，舉一反三，令人記起，689正是僭建豪宅的元祖，佢醒目過死蠢唐唐些少，拆得快好世界。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由過氣特首到律政司以至PK鄧與指揮官，他們的追隨者藍到海鮮開花，平時慣用海鮮諗嘢，食住個勢自編自導裝修工程，旁。。。。。。。。。。。多次，好奇一問，警察擴建俱樂部，點解購置四台泳褲脫水機？泳褲脫水，方便霸多忽官地嗎？689再出發，唔識跳閘，唯有勤力操練脫水剝褲，每日花八秒練習大叫「唔好搞我後面」，向去年6月11號金鐘站內疑似X X 的警長後院，致敬！ <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"b13f335fabad3e5a35a5107775d7254da5cfe141","tid":2004553,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T13:43:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">689係咪同志現形，戀上了肥佬黎？冇七成，都有五成吧。否則冇理由下下啄住肥佬黎背後，chur到盡，每日。。。。。。。。。。。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔敢想像 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}